config UHC_DWC2_ALIF
	bool "Alif Ensemble DWC2 USB host controller driver (SKELETON, bench-gated)"
	default y
	depends on DT_HAS_ALIF_DWC2_UHC_ENABLED
	depends on UHC_DRIVER
	help
	  SKELETON DWC2-host UHC driver for Alif Ensemble (E4/E6/E8).

	  The uhc_api op table, DT binding, register map (grounded from the
	  shared usb_dwc2_hw.h defines), and Kconfig are real.  Every host
	  bring-up path (bus reset, host-channel programming, transfer
	  completion, ISR) carries a TODO(aen401-bench) marker with the
	  intended DWC2 register sequence as a comment.

	  Do NOT enable this driver in production until the bench-gated paths
	  are filled in and validated on real AEN401 silicon.

	  Driver: zephyr/drivers/usb/uhc/uhc_dwc2_alif.c
	  Binding: zephyr/dts/bindings/usb/alif,dwc2-uhc.yaml
